<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900815-0015</DOCNO><DOCID>900815-0015.</DOCID><HL>   Rockwell Plans Shuttle Layoffs</HL><DATE>08/15/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   ROK</CO><LP>   EL SEGUNDO, Calif. -- Rockwell International Corp. said itwill lay off as many as 300 employees from its space-shuttleproduction and assembly facilities in Downey and Palmdale,Calif., by Sept. 30.   The layoffs come as production work on the Endeavourshuttle orbiter program is winding down, a Rockwell spokesmansaid.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>